{
  "stem": "13096.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were barges, you know, like usually, they hauled 22 crew of people, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But now, we were 1,750 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They squash all in these-- in these three barges, like 600 in each one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at board-- in board, were only three or four Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I must say, they were very good people, because they were not SS-- they were doing, you know, their military service.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were ordered to carry those passengers from one place, that Rhodes Island, to Greece, where the main quarters were.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they were very good to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were very good to us in the sense, because as we ate with us some provision that we are taking, you know, when the German order us to surrender-- so they allowed to use the small kitchen in the boat, you know, to cook, if we have.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then, even their own tea, they were giving to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then it was July.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "July in the Dodecanese, in those islands there, is very, very hot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then, we were not traveling at night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, there were, you know, the barges were stationary during the day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because they didn't want the-- the ally to spot us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then, you know, in the middle of July, if you were in those places, the sun is very, very hot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was very, you know, very uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So those Germans officer, they allowed everybody, if you want, to bathe in the sea.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We could have escaped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But where can you escape?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in any case, they were good to allowed us to-- to know, to-- to swim in the sea.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How old were you at this stage?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At this stage I was about 19.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was 19.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
